{"tid":1880734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣海巡署：你敢抽，我就賣","createTime":"2020-02-15T05:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T05:36:19.000Z","uid":91771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ef87e59f46f6978532d90a91a0379e2b18aef8f","tid":1880734,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"支那船呢排成日去台灣偷沙賣，今次就比台灣斷正<br />\n<br />\n人就罰款坐監，船就拎去拍賣，發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>台灣這個國家很簡單，你敢抽我們的砂，就拍賣你的船！<br />\n　<br />\n前幾個月，2艘來自中國的萬噸大船，侵門踏戶到我們的「台灣灘」海域，一艘抽砂、另一艘載砂，攜手犯罪、行徑猖狂；殊不知我們已大規模出動3艦3艇，配合空勤總隊，展開海空聯合執法。<br />\n　<br />\n事後2名船長以及25名船員，全都受澎湖地方法院宣告有期徒刑判決，並將在刑期、罰金繳清後遣返出境；而作為犯罪工具的「豐溢9969號」抽砂船及「長鑫36號」運砂船，恐難逃上架拍賣的命運。<br />\n　<br />\n昨天，艦隊分署派出2艦4艇，押著兩艘船移泊至興達港及高雄港，接下來，就等著二審宣判出爐，地檢署依法「公告拍賣」。<br />\n　<br />\n去年，我們扣下的抽砂船，分別賣到了「4819萬」、「2133萬」等超高單價，想必這次拍賣會也將大大增加國庫收益。<br />\n　<br />\n#你敢抽 #我敢賣<br />\n#有喜歡的按愛心❤️<br />\n#越界抽砂 #賣船拍賣<br />\n<br />\n海巡署艦隊分署<br />\n　<br />\n本案執法影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CGA4U/posts/2457233231269258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCGA4U%2Fposts%2F2457233231269258&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=3cdd0108\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CGA4U/posts/2457233231269258</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CGA4U/photos/a.2265883060404277/2566335550359025/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCGA4U%2Fphotos%2Fa.2265883060404277%2F2566335550359025%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=839eb36c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CGA4U/photos/a.2265883060404277/2566335550359025/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FGvfdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FGvfdk.jpg&h=19592b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲買埋個鬼仔張相嘅版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53533d0cda06982a15cff78da6b86b93d6ccbe99","tid":1880734,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"三跑又要超資延誤了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb8e8cf896f648f8b756b7ccd1ad9296b0088c","tid":1880734,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"樓主瞓咗幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}